            "creation_date": 1442388420,
            "body": "<p>You can try like this:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public static boolean findLetters() {\n    String text = \"HELLO HOW ARE YOU\";\n    String value = \"abc\";\n    for (int i = 0; i &lt; value.length(); i++) {\n        if (text.indexOf(value.toUpperCase().charAt(i)) == -1) {\n            return false;\n        }\n    }\n    return true;\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
